chunks.title: Business Hours
chunks.text: Our business is open from Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM. We are closed on weekends and public holidays.

chunks.title: Refund Policy
chunks.text: We offer a 30-day refund policy for all unused and undamaged products. Customers must provide proof of purchase to initiate a refund request.

chunks.title: Shipping Information
chunks.text: All orders are processed within 24 hours and delivered within 3 to 5 business days. Express shipping options are available at checkout for an additional fee.

chunks.title: Company Overview
chunks.text: We are a customer-focused technology company providing high-quality digital solutions, including AI-powered chatbots, automation systems, and cloud services.
